        {
            "title": "德黑蘭表示霍爾木茲海峽開放後 美元回吐伊朗戰爭以來全部漲幅",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美元抹去了自美伊戰爭爆發以來的全部漲幅，此前德黑蘭宣布霍爾木茲海峽已「完全向商業航運開放」，這進一步削弱了對避險資產的需求。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博美元即期指數下跌0.5%，至2月27日以來最低水平，延續此前跌勢，因投資者將注意力轉向停火以及達成更廣泛協議的可能性。周五，伊朗外長阿巴斯·阿拉格齊 在X上表示，在停火剩餘期間，商業船隻可以通過這一關鍵航道。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在衝突初期，由於投資者湧向避險資產、油價飆升，美元曾走強。然而，隨著宣布為期兩周的停火以及美伊官員釋放出願意進一步進行和平談判的信號，能源價格回落，投資者近期已轉向其他貨幣。周五，在伊朗表示這一關鍵石油運輸通道已向商業船隻開放後，美元指數跌勢進一步加速。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-e73d196d-d71b-3da4-bb1c-bd2fe0c05af4-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Dollar Wipes Out Iran War Gains as Tehran Says Hormuz Is Open</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%BE%B7%E9%BB%91%E8%98%AD%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E9%9C%8D%E7%88%BE%E6%9C%A8%E8%8C%B2%E6%B5%B7%E5%B3%BD%E9%96%8B%E6%94%BE%E5%BE%8C-%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E5%9B%9E%E5%90%90%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E6%88%B0%E7%88%AD%E4%BB%A5%E4%BE%86%E5%85%A8%E9%83%A8%E6%BC%B2%E5%B9%85-132648583.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-17 22:31:00",
