            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "瑞穗看好這檔主要AI晶片股",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/GtKneRkHTHKMYgJTDfJwvg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/asian_2_M_1440047814.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 瑞穗在與博通公司高層會面後,重申對其「優於大盤」評級,並指出定制AI晶片交易管道的加速發展是其主要收穫之一。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司分析師與博通執行長陳福陽、財務長Kirsten Spears及投資者關係主管Ji Yoo舉行投資者電話會議,對博通2027年及之後的AI營收軌跡更具信心。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">瑞穗強調了電話會議中的幾個關鍵要點,包括博通與Anthropic的TPU晶片部署相關的3.5吉瓦交易,預計將於2027年啟動。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-cb4c62ce-04f7-39d8-8fad-827311f4e039-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該券商認為,這項安排僅涵蓋TPU v8,「隨著後續TPU世代的推出,可能會有進一步的上升空間,推動後續交易。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">分析師還強調了博通與Meta Platforms的合作夥伴關係。該團隊提到Meta將其MTIA晶片的開發和部署擴展至2029年,涵蓋多個晶片世代和多吉瓦級建設。瑞穗估計,這些安排將為博通帶來每吉瓦約250億美元的助力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在網路方面,該券商認為,隨著下一代AI機架的擴展,博通將受益於向混合銅光纖部署的轉變。分析師認為,博通已在運行每通道400G-800G的SerDes技術,使銅纜能夠處理短距離機架連接,而光纖則在更長距離的應用中日益普及。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">然而,雷射供應仍然是一個限制因素。分析師表示,他們認為供應將「非常緊張」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">綜合來看,分析師認為博通2027年的AI營收共識預估將從2026年初的約1000億美元攀升至目前的約1200億美元,年增約62%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司預估2027財年AI營收為1010億美元,2028財年為1320億美元,三年複合年增長率達87%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">除了AI晶片,該團隊還指出VMware基礎設施軟體部門是另一個穩定支柱,被視為長期增長率在高個位數至低雙位數之間,營運利潤率約為80%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%91%9E%E7%A9%97%E7%9C%8B%E5%A5%BD%E9%80%99%E6%AA%94%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81ai%E6%99%B6%E7%89%87%E8%82%A1-131725592.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-17 21:35:20",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "賭注越押越大 希臘船東派出其迄今最大油輪穿越霍爾木茲海峽",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 一家希臘船東在伊朗戰爭期間多次讓其船隻冒險通過<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"霍爾木茲海峽\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:霍爾木茲海峽;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/霍爾木茲海峽\">霍爾木茲海峽</a>，如今又派出了自衝突爆發以來其最大的一艘超級油輪通過該航道。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博匯編數據顯示，這艘名為「Atokos」的超大型原油運輸船，運載能力約為200萬桶原油，周五在印度洋發出了位置信號。這表明，該船可能在過去幾天關閉了數字應答器，穿越了霍爾木茲海峽。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">行業數據庫顯示，這艘船由Dynacom Tankers Management Ltd.管理。此次航行意味著，該公司目前已通過霍爾木茲海峽運輸了約650萬桶原油，成為迄今為止經由該水道運輸量最大的非伊朗航運商。Dynacom未立即回應置評請求。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-09adcb09-8ff9-3de0-aeda-b96d20824fdb-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這條海峽在戰爭前承擔著全球約20%的石油運輸以及類似比例的液化天然氣運輸，如今的通行基本處於停滯狀態。這迫使該地區的生產商削減產量，同時也推高了原油以及航空燃油、柴油和汽油等成品油價格。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國本周也開始對伊朗航運實施封鎖，此舉疊加了自衝突爆發以來德黑蘭方面已實施的封鎖措施。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博匯編的船舶追蹤數據顯示，Atokos正駛往中國舟山港，預計將於5月5日抵達。該船在3月初於沙烏地拉斯塔努拉完成裝貨後不久，曾發出同一目的地信號，不過目前的預計到達時間比最初計畫晚了約六周。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Greek Shipowner Sends Biggest Oil Tanker Yet Through Hormuz (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">(新增最後一段目的地信息)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B3%AD%E6%B3%A8%E8%B6%8A%E6%8A%BC%E8%B6%8A%E5%A4%A7-%E5%B8%8C%E8%87%98%E8%88%B9%E6%9D%B1%E6%B4%BE%E5%87%BA%E5%85%B6%E8%BF%84%E4%BB%8A%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E6%B2%B9%E8%BC%AA%E7%A9%BF%E8%B6%8A%E9%9C%8D%E7%88%BE%E6%9C%A8%E8%8C%B2%E6%B5%B7%E5%B3%BD-123710124.html",
